data.meta_description: Jane Halighwell was born about 1486, daughter of Richard Halighwell and Jane Norbury. She was married in the year 1499 in Holwell, Bedfordshire, England to Edmund Braye, they gave birth to 1 child. She died on October 24, 1558. This information is part of Bacheler Family Tree by Steven Adrian Bacheler on Genealogy Online.
